io.github.nucleuspowered.nucleus.api.events

Interface NucleusFirstJoinEvent

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Event, MessageChannelEvent, MessageEvent, TargetEntityEvent, TargetHumanoidEvent, TargetLivingEvent, TargetPlayerEvent

    public interface NucleusFirstJoinEvent
extends TargetPlayerEvent, MessageChannelEvent
    Fired on a player's first time on the server.

    This will fire during ClientConnectionEvent.Join at the Order.LATE priority. Also note that these methods wrap around the ClientConnectionEvent.Join event methods, so any changes to these parameters will be fed back to the original event.
